<tr>
<td width="600" colspan="4">
<b>Description</b><br>
This robe is dropped by Ssynthi, a floating book which resides behind the crypt in the graveyard within Castle Mistmoore.  You will get bad faction with the Temple of Solusek Ro if you kill this monster, so you are warned.  If you have quest items that you would like to complete someday in the Temple, leave this creature alone.  It seems that Ssynthi drops the robe every time it dies.</td>
</tr>

